trans-unit.source: Azure API Management REST API Product Entity
trans-unit.target: Azure API Management REST API Product Entity

trans-unit.source: The Product entity represents a product in <token>azure_apimgt_3</token>.
trans-unit.target: The Product entity represents a product in <token>azure_apimgt_3</token>.

trans-unit.source: Products include one or more APIs and their associated terms of use.
trans-unit.target: Products include one or more APIs and their associated terms of use.

trans-unit.source: Once a product is published, developers can subscribe to the product and begin to use the product’s APIs.
trans-unit.target: Once a product is published, developers can subscribe to the product and begin to use the product’s APIs.
